      "description": "We are proud to present this extraordinary vehicle, preserved in pristine, showroom condition. Every detail of this motorcar reflects meticulous care and a steadfast commitment to mechanical excellence. This is a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a specimen of unrivaled aesthetic perfection and performance integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
