    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this car to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in truly pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels brand new! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for the road, this is the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 46500.0,
