      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with high-pressure VANOS and individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanically flawless, the subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been serviced to ensure peak longevity. The chassis remains rigid, supported by a precision-tuned suspension with no bushing play. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with zero rock chips or imperfections. A true purist\u2019s example with a documented service pedigree.",
